cards.title: Teen killed and seven injured in mass stabbing in Canada
cards.summary: 18-year-old woman killed and seven others injured in mass stabbing in Canada. The suspect also died in the attack at a First Nations community in Manitoba. Police said the suspect was fleeing the scene when he died in a vehicle collision.

cards.title: Hot mic catches Xi and Putin discussing organ transplants and immortality
cards.summary: Hot mic catches Xi and Putin discussing organ transplants and immortality. Putin suggested even eternal life could be achievable as a result of innovations in biotechnology. The unguarded moment was captured on a livestream carried by Chinese state TV as the two leaders walked together through China's historic Tiananmen Square.

cards.title: Boy, 3, pulled from funicular crash that has shocked Portugal
cards.summary: Boy, 3, pulled from funicular crash that has shocked Portugal. He was pulled from the carriage where his father reportedly died. His mother was among more than 20 other people who were injured.
